metadata.title: NPC snooker tournament reaches quarterfinal stage

content.article_body: ISLAMABAD, May 23 (APP):The National Press Club (NPC) Snooker tournament, which commenced on May 21, has entered the In the initial matches, Shafqat Saba booked his place in the quarterfinals after a solid victory over Javed Aslam. Ehtesham Kayani advanced with a win against Ashar Chaudhry, while Malik Asif triumphed overA Shafiq Awan in a closely contested match, said a press release. However, remaining to finalize the lineup for quarterfinal matches are scheduled to be played on Friday.
